files.file_name: Gladys the Corgi - A Custom Dog Follower Mod-50164-1-0-1-1622688043.zip
files.changelog_html:
Fixed issue where Gladys would be summoned whenever the player cast *any* spell.
When equipping George your left hand will now be lowered.
Added Immersive Interactions support out-of-the-box.

files.file_name: Gladys the Corgi - A Custom Dog Follower Mod-50164-1-2-0-1630558967.zip
files.changelog_html:
Added the ability to specify what you want Gladys to retrieve from the environment (weapon, armor, potion, lockpick, something valuable, or something random). Added a backpack option for Gladys' outfit. George will now be displayed in Gladys' mouth when he is in her inventory.
https://youtu.be/Nt48zrjgzZM Various small optimizations.
